- Update to version 2.3.1:
  * Various compatibility improvements.
  * New unit tests for Travis CI.
  * New --tar-extra, --untar-extra, --gpg-extra and
    --gpg-asymmetric-encrypt-sign options.
- Changes from version 2.3.0:
